
Building:

Set up the config file. Change the SRCROOT variable to point to the folder holding this file. Change
the USERNAME variable if you want fyodor to run as a user other than "fyodor"
Create a user that is the same name as USERNAME. Put it only in the users group to aviod potential
security holes.

Run install with root priveleges.
Login as the new user and run ./fetchmail and ./fyodor
